text:
With mosquito season right around the corner, you might be wondering if it's possible for mosquitoes to spread #COVID19. According to the @WHO, the new coronavirus CANNOT be transmitted through mosquito bites!

Learn more ➡️ https://t.co/28xWjk6P0L

#StayCalmStayHomeStaySafe https://t.co/5A1XlEJneB
